name: Multistrand Bracelets
description:
These gorgeous bracelets are made from a combination of Swarovski bicone crystals and Swarovski pearls. They come in 3 or 5 strands, in a number of color combinations. Each bracelet is about 8 inches long worn flat, and you can also wear it twisted for a different look, which will also tighten it. 

All items come in a kraft gift box, ready to give!

name: Hand Twisted Tree Necklace in Cherry Blossom
description:
These gorgeous necklaces feature 20 gauge vintage bronze colored copper wire wrapped into a tree, adorned with sparkling 4mm Swarovski crystals. The trees are then suspended from a wire-wrapped Swarovski crystal chain made with 6mm and 4mm crystals. The chain is finished off with a vintage bronze lobster clasp. The finished length is about 18 inches, and the tree will hang about 1 ½ to 2 inches below that. The chain can be made longer or shorter for no extra charge, simply leave a note in the Message to Seller upon checkout. Each tree is made to order, so they are all unique!

Pictured in this listing is the beautiful combination of fuchsia, rose and light rose. Please allow up to 2 weeks for completion, based on color availability.

All items come in a kraft gift box, ready to give!

description:

name: Hand Twisted Set in Wedding Crystal and Pearl
description:
This amazing set features a Hand Twisted Tree Necklace, Crystal Wrapped Bracelet, and Branch Earrings. Each piece is hand-wrapped using German silver plated wire and sparkling Swarovski crystals, and finished off with a silver plated clasp and sterling silver French hooks. The necklace measures about 18 inches, the bracelet about 7 ¼ inches, and the earrings measure 1 ½ inches and are incredibly lightweight! Each set is made to order, so each piece is unique! A perfect set for your special day. 

Pictured in this listing is the beautiful combination of clear crystals and Swarovski pearls. Please allow up to 2 weeks for completion, based on color availability. 

All items come in a kraft gift box, ready to give!
